CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1777014325
OL,3,CJury discharged in alleged baby murder
OL,4,Ctrial
OL,6,FThe trial of two men accused over the
OL,7,Falleged murder and sexual abuse of an
OL,8,Fadopted baby boy has been stopped and
OL,9,Fthe jury discharged.
OL,11,FFormer high school teacher Jamie
OL,12,FVarley, 37, is accused of the murder
OL,13,Fof 13-month-old Preston Davey, along
OL,14,Fwith 25 other charges relating to his
OL,15,Fsexual abuse, physical mistreatment
OL,16,Fand taking of indecent images.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
