OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1777014325
OL,3,CJury discharged in alleged baby murder
OL,4,Ctrial
OL,6,FHis partner, John McGowan-Fazakerley,
OL,7,F32, is accused of causing or allowing
OL,8,Fthe death of the child and four other
OL,9,Foffences including sexual assault and
OL,10,Fcruelty.
OL,12,FBoth men deny all charges, between
OL,13,FMarch and 27 July 2023.
OL,15,FOn the fourth day of the trial at
OL,16,FPreston Crown Court, the jury of six
OL,17,Fwomen and six men were brought into
OL,18,Fcourt and discharged from sitting any
OL,19,Ffurther and proceedings halted by
OL,20,Ftrial judge Mr Justice Mark Turner.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1777014325
OL,3,CJury discharged in alleged baby murder
OL,4,Ctrial
OL,6,FHe told jurors: "I regret to say the
OL,7,Freason for the delay in starting today
OL,8,Fis that circumstances have arisen
OL,9,Fwhich make it impossible for this
OL,10,Ftrial to continue now.
OL,12,F"I commend the obvious attention and
OL,13,Fconcentration you have exercised over
OL,14,Fthe last few days and you have
OL,15,Fperformed your duty without any sort
OL,16,Fof criticism of any of you at all.
OL,26,@nD@QOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1777014325
OL,3,CJury discharged in alleged baby murder
OL,4,Ctrial
OL,6,F"I am afraid I have been left with no
OL,7,Freasonable alternative but to
OL,8,Fdischarge you from this trial. You are
OL,9,Fnot permitted to discuss this case
OL,10,Fwith anyone or post on social media or
OL,11,Fbe in any communication about what
OL,12,Fhappened during your time together,
OL,13,Fnow and forever.
OL,15,F"Thank you very much again but with a
OL,16,Fheavy heart, I discharge you."
OL,18,FThe reason for discharging the jury is
OL,19,Fnot reportable.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOUxD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
