PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1777014325
OL,3,CJury discharged in alleged baby murder
OL,4,Ctrial
OL,6,FPreston had been taken into care by
OL,7,FOldham Council shortly after his birth
OL,8,Fin June 2022 and lived with foster
OL,9,Fparents until April 2023, when he was
OL,10,Fadopted by the defendants, living at
OL,11,Ftheir home on Staining Road, Blackpool.
OL,13,FEarlier in the trial, which began on
OL,14,FMonday, Peter Wright KC, prosecuting,
OL,15,Fsaid in the just under four months the
OL,16,Fchild was in the defendants' care he
OL,17,Fhad been routinely ill-treated, had
OL,18,Findecent images and videos taken of
OL,19,Fhim, had been sexually abused and
OL,20,Fphysically assaulted, suffering 40
OL,21,Ftraumatic injuries.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
