PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1777014325
OL,3,CJury discharged in alleged baby murder
OL,4,Ctrial
OL,6,FOn 27 July 2023, Preston was rushed to
OL,7,FBlackpool Victoria Hospital by the
OL,8,Fdefendants, unconscious and in a state
OL,9,Fof cardiac arrest and died shortly
OL,10,Fafterwards.
OL,12,FVarley told police he had left the
OL,13,Fchild in the bath and minutes later
OL,14,Freturned to find him drowning, Preston
OL,15,FCrown Court heard.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
