PN,39907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1777014325
OL,3,CJury discharged in alleged baby murder
OL,4,Ctrial
OL,6,FMr Wright said this explanation was
OL,7,Finconsistent with the evidence from
OL,8,Fthe post-mortem, which found multiple
OL,9,Fnon-accidental, internal and external
OL,10,Finjuries and gave a cause of death as
OL,11,Feither smothering or the insertion of
OL,12,Fan object or objects into the
OL,13,Fyoungster's mouth.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
