PN,39908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1777014325
OL,3,CJury discharged in alleged baby murder
OL,4,Ctrial
OL,6,FVarley denies murder, manslaughter,
OL,7,Ftwo counts of assault by penetration,
OL,8,Ffive counts of cruelty to a child,
OL,9,Fgrievous bodily harm, sexual assault
OL,10,Fof a child, 13 counts of taking
OL,11,Findecent photos or videos of a child,
OL,12,Fone of distributing an indecent photo
OL,13,Fof a child, to his co-accused, and one
OL,14,Fof making an indecent photo.
OL,16,FMcGowan-Fazakerley denies allowing the
OL,17,Fdeath of a child, three counts of
OL,18,Fchild cruelty and one count of the
OL,19,Fsexual assault of a child.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
